===Etymology===
From {{inh|en|enm|brekefast}}, {{m|enm|brekefaste}}, equivalent to {{compound|en|break|fast}} {{gloss|''literally'', "to end the nightly fast"}}, likely a variant of {{inh|en|ang|fæstenbryċe}}, {{gloss|''literally'', "fast-breach"}}. Cognate with {{cog|nl|breekvasten|t=breakfast}}.

